    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Documents, usually sealed, granting specific rights, setting forth aims and principles of a newly established entity, and often embodying formal agreements and authorizing special privileges or exemptions.</Note_Text>
